import seaborn as sns
import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    data = data.copy()
    data['Penicillin'] = pd.to_numeric(data['Penicillin'], errors='coerce')
    sns.set(style="whitegrid")
    chart = sns.boxplot(x="Penicillin", data=data, color='blue')
    chart.axvline(data['Penicillin'].median(), color='red', label='Median: {:.2f}'.format(data['Penicillin'].median()))
    chart.legend()
    plt.title('What is the distribution of Penicillin across all bacteria?', wrap=True)
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)

    return plt;
